Agar hum large webpage ka sara code ek hi file me likhen, toh bahut problems hoti hain:

Code bahut bada aur confusing ho jata hai.
Bugs dhundhna difficult ho jata hai.
Reusability nahi hoti, same code baar-baar likhna padta hai.
Team me kaam karna hard ho jata hai because sab ek hi file edit karte hain.
Maintenance aur updates difficult ho jate hain.
Readability kam ho jati hai.
Project scalable nahi rehta for large applications.

Isliye React me webpage ko small reusable components me divide kiya jata hai jaise:

Header
Navbar
Hero Section
Card
Footer

Is approach se code:

clean
reusable
manageable
scalable

ban jata hai.